    "description": "欢迎来到《电子幻术》——引人入胜的像素风格微恐解谜游戏，带你探索千禧年间虚拟现实项目！<br>电子幻术是21世纪首个虚拟现实游乐项目，凭借其带给用户极具创造力的新奇体验，在千禧年间红极一时。但后续因遭受恶意谣传与病毒感染等种种原因，公司被迫关闭了这一项目。而现在已经荒废的电子幻术仪器将被重新启动……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/be1b50e235affde69e02806722a6d34e.poster.avif?t=1751066899\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/be1b50e235affde69e02806722a6d34e.webm?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/be1b50e235affde69e02806722a6d34e.mp4?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>在游戏中，你将通过鼠标操控场景中的物件/家具，解锁不同关卡的谜题。这种通过改变实体场景来解谜的独特玩法，为你带来全新的体验与乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/f2dd241c44a80fdf3bafacef8d88de74.poster.avif?t=1751066899\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/f2dd241c44a80fdf3bafacef8d88de74.webm?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/f2dd241c44a80fdf3bafacef8d88de74.mp4?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏结合了千禧复古风格的场景设计，营造出神秘而引人入胜的氛围。精致的像素艺术风格和独特的数据化故障表现，将唤起你对过去的怀旧情感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/44948c7ca0d8975fe833928f990d4af1.poster.avif?t=1751066899\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/44948c7ca0d8975fe833928f990d4af1.webm?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109800/extras/44948c7ca0d8975fe833928f990d4af1.mp4?t=1751066899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>通过丰富的场景、多媒体元素和显示屏叙事，游戏将呈现出主角在电子幻术世界中的内心挣扎与奇妙遭遇。你需要拼凑这些碎片化的画面，感受欲望和恐惧交织的故事。",
